328
00:14:28,291 --> 00:14:30,375
<i>Fierce-Soccer</i> ?
Cool, let me see!

329
00:14:30,458 --> 00:14:31,666
Huh?!

330
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:34,500
Uh, but I haven't read it yet.

331
00:14:34,583 --> 00:14:36,250
[TAKAGI] Can I at
least see the front cover?

332
00:14:36,333 --> 00:14:37,708
[NISHIKATA]
No!

333
00:14:37,791 --> 00:14:39,416
'Cuz I haven't had a chance
to look at it yet, either.

334
00:14:39,500 --> 00:14:40,500
