335
00:14:40,583 --> 00:14:41,833
[TAKAGI]
Then, let's look at it together.

336
00:14:41,916 --> 00:14:44,125
[NISHIKATA] I happen
to like looking at it alone.

337
00:14:44,208 --> 00:14:45,500
Awww...

338
00:14:45,583 --> 00:14:46,583
[NISHIKATA] I wouldn't
have thought she'd be

339
