346
00:15:03,458 --> 00:15:05,000
Let's walk together.

347
00:15:05,083 --> 00:15:06,583
[NISHIKATA]
Okay, fine.

348
00:15:07,666 --> 00:15:09,208
[TAKAGI] It's pretty unusual
to run into someone

349
00:15:09,291 --> 00:15:13,125
