home this early in the morning.

350
00:15:14,791 --> 00:15:16,500
[NISHIKATA] I can't let
Takagi see this manga

351
00:15:16,583 --> 00:15:19,291
and yet here it is, three feet
from her in my backpack!

352
00:15:19,375 --> 00:15:21,416
