364
00:15:45,250 --> 00:15:47,458
It's just some
manga for girls, right?

365
00:15:47,541 --> 00:15:50,125
<i>100% Unrequited Love</i> ?

366
00:15:50,208 --> 00:15:52,333
[NISHIKATA] Okay. There's no
point in denying it now, but...

367
00:15:52,416 --> 00:15:55,500
...how in the world
did you figure it out?

368
00:15:55,583 --> 00:15:56,458
Just luck.

369
00:15:56,541 --> 00:15:57,708
I happened to be passing by

370
00:15:57,791 --> 00:15:59,875
