372
00:16:01,875 --> 00:16:04,375
[NISHIKATA] She knew the
whole time and was playing me.

373
00:16:04,458 --> 00:16:05,833
[TAKAGI] Is it because
you like the anime?

374
00:16:05,916 --> 00:16:07,958
