400
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:56,750
Huh?

401
00:16:56,833 --> 00:16:58,708
I guess.

402
00:16:58,791 --> 00:16:59,583
[TAKAGI]
All right.

403
00:16:59,666 --> 00:17:00,875
