404
00:17:00,958 --> 00:17:04,041
[NISHIKATA]
Okay.

405
00:17:04,125 --> 00:17:07,833
Truth is I've always
kind of liked you.

406
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,333
[NISHIKATA]
Huh?

407
00:17:13,750 --> 00:17:15,166
[NISHIKATA]
