to you as payback.

415
00:17:30,375 --> 00:17:31,583
[NISHIKATA]
Oh, a lie.

416
00:17:31,666 --> 00:17:33,458
You shocked me for a second.

417
00:17:33,541 --> 00:17:34,875
That was a lie.

418
00:17:34,958 --> 00:17:37,666
Of course it was. Duh, right?

419
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:38,625
See yah!

420
00:17:38,708 --> 00:17:40,458
I'm turning this way now.

421
00:17:40,541 --> 00:17:41,833
