423
00:17:45,375 --> 00:17:47,125
A lie, huh?

424
00:17:47,875 --> 00:17:49,750
[TAKAGI]
Oh, and Nishikata?

425
00:17:49,833 --> 00:17:52,583
I want to read
<i>100% Unrequited Love</i> too,

426
00:17:52,666 --> 00:17:55,375
