it so loud, Takagi!

429
00:18:02,541 --> 00:18:04,750
[NISHIKATA]
"Shelter from the Rain."

430
00:18:06,791 --> 00:18:09,625
This downpour
came out of nowhere.

431
00:18:09,708 --> 00:18:11,750
