432
00:18:11,833 --> 00:18:12,625
[NISHIKATA]
Hmm...

433
00:18:12,708 --> 00:18:14,125
Well, I hope so.

434
00:18:15,625 --> 00:18:18,791
[TAKAGI] Aww.
Even my socks got wet.

435
00:18:18,875 --> 00:18:19,833
[NISHIKATA gasps]

436
00:18:19,916 --> 00:18:21,291
[TAKAGI]
