437
00:18:21,375 --> 00:18:24,125
[NISHIKATA] Oh man, I can
kinda see through her shirt.

438
00:18:25,166 --> 00:18:26,166
You hear me?

439
00:18:26,250 --> 00:18:27,833
Uh. Yeah, I heard you.

440
00:18:27,916 --> 00:18:28,625
Yeah.

441
00:18:28,708 --> 00:18:30,125
