511
00:20:55,625 --> 00:20:57,208
[NISHIKATA] Are you trying
to get out of the rain?

512
00:20:57,291 --> 00:20:58,750
[TAKAGI]
Come here.

513
00:20:58,833 --> 00:21:00,625
He's cute, but be careful.

514
00:21:00,708 --> 00:21:02,083
He scratches.

515
00:21:05,333 --> 00:21:07,250
Do you want me to give
you your shirt back?

516
00:21:07,333 --> 00:21:08,833
No. I'm fine.

517
00:21:10,916 --> 00:21:12,916
[TAKAGI] Why don't
you wear my P.E. shirt?

518
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:13,833
Huh?

519
00:21:13,916 --> 00:21:15,000
[TAKAGI]
It did get a little wet,

520
00:21:15,083 --> 00:21:17,083
but it's better than
what you've got on.

521
00:21:18,041 --> 00:21:19,500
[NISHIKATA]
And now,

522
00:21:19,583 --> 00:21:23,333
The shirt that touched Takagi's
skin will be touching mine.

523
00:21:23,416 --> 00:21:24,458
Are you done yet?

524
00:21:24,541 --> 00:21:25,958
[gasps]

525
00:21:26,041 --> 00:21:28,583
[NISHIKATA] Come on,
you're not supposed to look!

526
00:21:29,083 --> 00:21:32,916
[NISHIKATA] For some reason
this feels naughty.

527
00:21:35,291 --> 00:21:37,375
[NISHIKATA]
It smells good.

528
00:21:48,458 --> 00:21:50,541
[TAKAGI]
I guess I win.

529
00:21:50,625 --> 00:21:52,333
What should I make you do?

530
00:21:53,458 --> 00:21:54,958
[NISHIKATA]
Oh, well.

531
00:21:55,041 --> 00:21:57,375
At least, <i>Fierce-Soccer</i> 'll
be on when I get home.

532
00:21:57,458 --> 00:21:59,625
I'll do what she wants
and hurry back.

533
00:21:59,708 --> 00:22:00,750
[TAKAGI]
Oh, I know!

534
00:22:00,833 --> 00:22:02,000
[NISHIKATA]
Huh?

535
00:22:02,708 --> 00:22:04,000
Now that it's stopped raining,

536
00:22:04,083 --> 00:22:05,791
let's go somewhere
before we head home.

537
00:22:05,875 --> 00:22:07,333
[NISHIKATA]
Wait, I wanted to--

538
00:22:07,416 --> 00:22:09,791
[TAKAGI] The bet was, the loser
does what the winner wants!

539
00:22:09,875 --> 00:22:10,708
Let's go.

540
00:22:10,791 --> 00:22:12,333
[NISHIKATA]
Why?!

